&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A draft PEP that proposes adding a new fully persistent and immutable mapping type called frozenmap to the collections module in the Python standard library.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;(&lt;code&gt;是也乎:&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
